                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18351214-261-offence-1 t18351214-cd-62"></join>14th of September</rs>, 9lbs. of soap, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18351214-name-478" type="victimName">
